HEADWORD: Prestidigitator
<hw>Pres`ti*dig"i*ta`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>praesto</ets> ready + <ets>digitus</ets> finger: cf. F.
<ets>prestidigitateur</ets>.]</ety> <def>One skilled in legerdemain or
sleight of hand; a juggler.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

